
Welcome
Dear student, we are pleased to have you join us on this transformational journey to being a data scientist. As your
Sensei we will guide you through the fundamentals of Python programming. Whether you are completely new to
coding or looking to sharpen your skills, this course is designed to provide you with the building blocks you need to
becorne a Data Scientist.
This is is the program is divided into 16 weeks (4 months) comprehensive learning process and 32 weeks (8 months) for
real-world capstone projects. It is made up of 6 modules namely:
